title: Grano Frutta e Farina
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Italian, Mediterranean, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Little takeaway bakery and deli with a couple tables for eating-in. Offers a large selection of baked goods as well prepared foods, has smoothies. Also sells nuts, seeds, and dried fruit.
